PHP laravel for bank complaint system

In a bank complaint system, a customer can input a complaint, where the support person is able to resolve their issue.

Considered Options
PHP Laravel
Python-Django
C#-ASP.NET core
…
Decision Outcome
Chosen option: "PHP Laravel", because it has built in tool for authentivcation and routing, which is a significant part of this complaint system. It also has good ORM with the database which is ideal as the complaint system is constantly fetching data from the database.

Consequences
Good, because it has good scalability and extensibility.
Bad, because can be slow if not properly optimised. 
